  "description": "<section class=\"xmteditor\" style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section class=\"xmteditor\" style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<p>准备参加四六级口语考试的同学，历年真题是必不可少的宝贵材料。阁主（微信：hujiangcet）给大家整理了2017年5月最全的四六级口语考试真题，一起来看看吧~</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin: 10px 0%;\">\n<section style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); border-radius: 5px;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 5px; height: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-right: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); float: left; border-top-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 5px; height: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); float: right; border-top-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); border-right-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"clear: both;\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"padding-right: 4px; padding-left: 4px;\">\n<section>\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; border-width: 0.1em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; float: left; border-bottom: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 2.4em; height: 2.3em; border-top: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; line-height: 3.2em;\">\n<section style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(74, 62, 62);\">\n<p><strong>写</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; border-width: 0.1em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; float: left; border-bottom: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 2.4em; height: 2.3em; border-top: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; line-height: 3.2em;\">\n<section style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(74, 62, 62);\">\n<p><strong>在</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; border-width: 0.1em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; float: left; border-bottom: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 2.4em; height: 2.3em; border-top: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; line-height: 3.2em;\">\n<section style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(74, 62, 62);\">\n<p><strong>前</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; border-width: 0.1em; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;\">\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 1.5em; height: 1.5em; float: left; border-bottom: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 2.4em; height: 2.3em; border-top: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224); border-right: 0.1em solid rgb(239, 239, 224);\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 3.2em; height: 3.2em; line-height: 3.2em;\">\n<section style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(74, 62, 62);\">\n<p><strong>面</strong></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;\">\n<section style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(105, 104, 104); line-height: 1.8;\">\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2017年上半年的四六级口试已经在5月20日和5月21日落下帷幕~&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">这次口语考试题目和16年12月的作文题目一样，<strong><span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\">涉猎甚广</span></strong>。</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">必考的校园生活考查范围由浅及深，小到学校里<strong>PPT制作、电子支付，大到探讨高等教育的利弊</strong>。</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">当然，口试话题也考查了一些<strong>比较严肃的话题</strong>：如四级口试让考生讨论<strong>消除贫困（这不是某年四级翻译的题目么）、老龄化现象</strong>、有的同学还抽到了<strong>孩子教育、预算</strong>这类话题。</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">而六级则集中在<strong>人文关怀类话题</strong>上，比如摔倒的老人该不该扶？高科技对英语学习的帮助等等，真题会在下面一一列出，此处不赘述。</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">由此可见，<span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>四六级口试所考话题涉猎甚广，需要积累各种topic的基础词汇（这个靠大家死记硬背了），但讨论的展开方式却有迹可循</strong></span>。</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #8d8d8d;\">原文中此处为链接，暂不支持采集</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">所以！复习口语和复习四六级考试最好同步进行，举一反三，活学活用，才能百战不殆，笑傲考场~&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">接下来，看看阁主整理的【最全】四六级口试真题吧<span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>（四级12个topic，六级9个topic）</strong></span>~ &nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong>本文主要内容：</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">第一部分：2017年5月四级口语考试真题</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">第二部分：2017年5月六级口语考试真题</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong>阅读须知：</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">四六级口试各有10多个话题（本文基本全部覆盖到了），<span style=\"color: #2F8A4D;\"><strong>一般会要求先围绕这个话题做自我陈述，陈述完毕后，再和你的partner进行小组讨论</strong></span>。四六级小组讨论的时间不同，六级要求讨论更深入。</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">最后，题目多为考生回忆，部分话题可能只有一个part的题目或只有中/英文，见谅啦~ 阁主后续会实时更新的~</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section style=\"width: 5px; height: 5px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-right: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); float: left; border-bottom-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 5px; height: 5px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left: 1px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); float: right; border-right-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); border-bottom-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"clear: both;\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n<section style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom;\">\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77); padding: 0.2em 0.4em; text-align: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;\">\n<p style=\"clear: none;\"><strong>2017年5月<span style=\"color: #000000;\">【<strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">四级</strong>】</span>口语考试真题</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 0px; float: left; border-right: 5px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-top: 3px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left: 5px solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent !important;\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 0px; float: right; border-left: 5px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-top: 3px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-right: 5px solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent !important;\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一、 旅游</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. Where to go and how to go</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2. what to take</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3. what to do</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: #8d8d8d;\">原文中此处为链接，暂不支持采集</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">二、PPT</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">PPT的制作方法和技巧</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>小组讨论：</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">What should be presented in my PPT?</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何用PPT展现一堂课</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">三、自由工作时间制</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">公司应不应该采用自由工作时间制</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; background-color: #EFEFEF;\">whether companies are adopting flexible working time</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">公司应不应该采用自由工作时间，</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">说明理由（要点如下）：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1.total working hour</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.core working hour</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3.your daily flexible working hour assignment</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">四、软饮料（soft drinks）</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">年轻人喜欢喝软饮料的原因</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就这个话题，阁主给大家找了一个范例参考：</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Soft drinks are called &quot;soft&quot; in contrast to &quot;hard drinks&quot; which usually contain alcohol. The taste of soft drink is so great that teenagers like it, especially in summer or in the environment of high temperature. What&rsquo;smore, in some parties, soft drink is the most choice for young people because of its limited influence in people&rsquo;s security in both physical and mental health. In addition to this, youngsters choose soft drink as their daily drinkfor its convenience, </span><a name=\"OLE_LINK3\" style=\"font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">especially during the travels or sometrips</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">.</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #888888; font-size: 14px;\">（来源：文都教育）</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">关于软饮料的小组讨论，题目要求从以下3个方面说起，&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. 软饮料的危害</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2. 政府怎么规范软饮料的销售</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3. 商家如何提高软饮料的健康指数。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">五、Language（<strong style=\"white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">语言</span></strong>）</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">the future of the Chinese language in a globalized world</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：Language</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. hiring teachers</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2. teaching materials</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3. finding suitable place</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">六、摆脱贫困的方法</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">The most effective method to fight against poverty</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">摆脱贫困的方法</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">七、高等教育</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：高等教育的裨益</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">the reasons why you choose your major</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">选择这个专业的原因</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">八、健康</span></strong></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1. &nbsp;rational diet&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2. &nbsp;sufficient rest and proper exercise</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3. &nbsp;optimistic attitude</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">九、 老龄化现象</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Ways to cope with anaging society</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">十、 论预算/省钱的重要性</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Describe the importance of having a budget.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可以展开说saving money的好处和重要性</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">十一、家庭教育</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">How to educate your child?&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如何教育你的孩子？</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">十二、 沟通</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">The importance of communication skills</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px; background-color: #EFEFEF;\">沟通技巧的重要性</span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZlMGlhTmp5YVVTaWNsbE1pYzZvTGFKdFlLSWRnckU0eE0zbjZwTWo5OTNMU0RNRWJuS09ublhSeVh2MGZSM1RmQndQWDRqZnk1clNSRmljZy8w\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<section style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n<section style=\"width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom;\">\n<section style=\"padding: 0.2em 0.4em; text-align: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(47, 138, 77);\">\n<p style=\"clear: none;\"><strong>2017年5月<span style=\"color: #000000;\">【六级】</span>口语考试真题</strong></p>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 0px; float: left; border-right: 5px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-top: 3px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-left: 5px solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent !important;\">&nbsp;</section>\n\n<section style=\"width: 0px; float: right; border-left: 5px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-top: 3px solid rgb(47, 138, 77); border-right: 5px solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 3px solid transparent !important;\">&nbsp;</section>\n</section>\n\n<section>\n<section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\">\n<section>\n<section>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一、高科技和英语学习</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #EFEFEF; font-size: 15px;\">高科技对英语学习的帮助</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">hightechnology plays an important role in English study</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高科技在课堂教学中是不是必不可少？</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Is High-techis&nbsp;definitely indispensible in class teaching?</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">二、校园养宠物</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Your Attitude Towards Keeping Pets on Campus</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你对校园养宠物的态度</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">pets on campus: the importance of protecting animals&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">校园养宠物：保护动物的重要性</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">三、电子支付</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述： 谈论对电子支付的看法</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：E-pay</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">四、优秀领导的特质</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">What makes a good leader&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">优秀领导的特质</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Is It Better to Lead or to Be Led?</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">成为领导者和被领导哪个更好</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">五、看图论述：人与人之间的信任</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">题目给出的是一张图片，图片上所画的内容是：一个老人摔倒，有一个女士路过走开，有两个男士则要求签写证明之后再扶起老人。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该环节要求考生描述图片中的内容，然后给出自己的做法。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">扶老人是我们的责任吗？</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Is&nbsp;ifting up the old our responsibility?</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">六、家庭关系</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">The Reasons Accounting for Changes of Family Relationships</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">家庭关系改变的原因</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Will the family relationship as close as before?&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">家庭关系是否如之前一样亲密？</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">七、医疗</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">the importance of medical treatment</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">谈论医疗的重要性</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">medical overuse 过度医疗</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">八、互相帮助</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;The Importance of Helping Each Other in Daily Life</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">生活中互相帮助的重要性</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Why Should Rich People Be Encouraged to Donate?</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为什么应该鼓励富人捐赠？</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">九、机器人</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">个人陈述：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">the increasing&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;robots</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">机器人的使用</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">小组讨论：</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Will&nbsp;robots&nbsp;one day replace people to control the world?</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">机器人能否控制世界?</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以上就是今天的主要内容了~</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">周末参加考试的小伙伴，来讨论区说说你们都考到了什么题目吧~&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">给阁主留言哦~~&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"http://image2.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpel9qcGcvaWE2cDlDWG5VYmZjWkZtY3FoYktYd1hhakZkM1VtdGppYXJrS0tQNWNVeWliV2liV2J4Q0JOVnE0cktacHBZYTBmcEhjSkFHS2h3RFRKaWNUUjFJWGYwWjBSdy8w\" style=\"float: left;\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span 